OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA dry start with some
OL,6,Fbrightness, but turning mostly cloudy
OL,7,Fthrough the morning with outbreaks of
OL,8,Frain, heaviest and most persistent
OL,9,Facross western parts through the
OL,10,Fafternoon.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FIt will be mostly cloudy in
OL,13,Fthe evening with outbreaks of rain.
OL,14,FStaying cloudy overnight with further
OL,15,Frain, heavy and perhaps thundery at
OL,16,Ftimes.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
