OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FCloud and occasionally heavy,
OL,6,Fshowery overnight rain soon clearing.
OL,7,FThen sunny spells and scattered
OL,8,Fshowers, occasionally heavy with a
OL,9,Fchance of thunder.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FMainly
OL,12,Fdry and bright Monday morning with
OL,13,Fsunny spells, cloud and outbreaks of
OL,14,Frain later. Mostly cloudy Tuesday and
OL,15,FWednesday with rain or showers, heavy
OL,16,Fand thundery at times.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
